{"tid":979845,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020美國總統大選，安潔莉納裘莉對戰川普？——「只要能幫助世界改變，我願意做任何事」","createTime":"2019-01-13T05:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T07:45:54.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c13e112a42542ce1326ede79dbc3d151095c2afa","tid":979845,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T05:06:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/gettyimages-1071531486.jpg?crop=1.00xw:0.753xh;0,0.152xh&amp;resize=980:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2Fgettyimages-1071531486.jpg%3Fcrop%3D1.00xw%3A0.753xh%3B0%2C0.152xh%26resize%3D980%3A%2A&h=a4964826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日，安潔莉娜裘莉於BBC Radio 4 Today受訪時，被問及是否會參選美國2020總統大選，裘莉竟並未把話給說死？！裘莉曾是最會賺錢的好萊塢女星，名聲錢財都不缺的她，近年將重心轉移至推動人道計畫。擔任聯合國難民署特使後，她意識到若要改變世界需要依靠政治的幫忙，因此不排除未來要進入政壇的可能。<br />\n美國2020年總統大選<br />\n在BBC訪談中，裘莉表示自己現在對待政治的觀點，和以往很不同：「如果在20年前，你問我願不願意從政，我可能就只是微笑帶過，不確定自己是否適合，但我現在對政治的想法很開放，只要能幫助世界改變，我願意做任何事，只要能帶來實際的行動，我可以和政府或甚至軍隊合作。」<br />\n美國下一屆的總統大選，將在2020年11月舉行，BBC的主持人說，裘莉的名字很適合出現在總統候選人名單上，而裘莉只簡短地回答一句謝謝，但隨後她也繼續補充自己的想法，雖然沒有直接回應問題，卻也沒有把話說死。<br />\n積極的提倡者<br />\n43歲的裘莉，不僅僅只是名好萊塢女星，充滿同理心的她更長期致力參與弱勢族群、性別平權等推廣活動。曾與英國前外交部長赫格（William Hague）共同提出「預防性暴力倡議」（Preventing Sexual Violence in Conflict Initiative），為相關議題發聲。<br />\n女王頒授勳章<br />\n2014年在白金漢宮，英國女王伊莉莎白二世，為了表揚裘莉對女權、戰區難民議題的貢獻，特別頒授聖米迦勒及聖喬治勳章給裘莉，並給予榮譽女爵士的頭銜。<br />\n感謝裘莉積極為女性、弱勢孩童、難民發聲，希望透過她的引響力，引起世界關注相關議題，也許未來真的有機會，可以看到裘莉投身政壇。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.harpersbazaar.com/tw/celebrity/celebritynews/g25773792/angelina-jolie-us-presidency/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.harpersbazaar.com%2Ftw%2Fcelebrity%2Fcelebritynews%2Fg25773792%2Fangelina-jolie-us-presidency%2F&d=jgQC4nYOMPLA6sKQfMlIGePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=ac6d262e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.harpersbazaar.com/tw/celebrity/celebritynews/g25773792/angelina-jolie-us-presidency/</a>"},{"pid":"835fcdd7aef5df90c908f97cda2642a950e4fbcc","tid":979845,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T05:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a40ecf471ef3073386b64d04473bca2458a99d","tid":979845,"uid":222140,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T05:09:17.000Z","msg":"安潔乜撚柒嘢。。<br />\n負評，上一頁。"},{"pid":"3fe7d30d44b713507468413b45771f659cdc82c4","tid":979845,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T05:11:17.000Z","msg":"好事黎<br />\n佢對戰侵即係侵贏撚硬"},{"pid":"1e597aa07003c470ae82b551bef5b73f1bcd7277","tid":979845,"uid":121146,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T05:11:21.000Z","msg":"為左幫侵侵連任可以去到幾盡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d584a8efc297fddbe24be97487e1d5ebc051d34f","tid":979845,"uid":56453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T05:13:48.000Z","msg":"第二個列根真係咁易有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4103ee34e489806a31bbf319d7120e85fcf77d8","tid":979845,"uid":211461,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T05:45:31.000Z","msg":"安祖蓮娜祖莉 幾時改左名"},{"pid":"1ba303ca2d72a6e7b6ebd4da56a734113b6940f9","tid":979845,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T05:48:06.000Z","msg":"荷里活左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a62d02ad3127fef7821bdf4206944aaf2faf372","tid":979845,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T05:55:37.000Z","msg":"邊撚個叫安潔乜乜乜鳩"},{"pid":"7159090ece640e037b807618cde40b285e2cb07a","tid":979845,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ba303ca2d72a6e7b6ebd4da56a734113b6940f9","tid":979845,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T05:48:06.000Z","msg":"荷里活左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/